1. Please Create a database named grievence
2. Run the Following Queries in that database
	
	CREATE TABLE users (
    id INT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT,
    username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    password VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    role varchar(50) NOT NULL,
    created_at DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
	);
	
	CREATE TABLE complaints(name varchar(100),
                        email varchar(50),
                        token int(5),
                        level varchar(30),
                        subcategory varchar(40),
                        complaint varchar(100000),
                        status varchar(30),
                        comments varchar(5000));
						
3. Once you Sign up Go to database and assign roles
4. home.php is the main file Run this file in browser